      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-102"><xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpSecurity.Mode%2A>가 메시지 수준에서 클라이언트 인증을 수행하도록 구성된 경우 이 열거형은 클라이언트 자격 증명 형식을 제어합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-102">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpSecurity.Mode%2A> is configured to perform client authentication at the message level, this enumeration controls the client credential type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-103"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> 확장성 지점을 구현하는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityCredentialsManager> 인스턴스를 통해 사용할 username 및 X.509 인증서를 제공해야 합니다. 일반적인 경우 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-103">Both username and X.509 certificate to use must be provisioned through an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> instance which implements the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityCredentialsManager> extensibility point; in a common default case this is <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-104">인증서의 경우 클라이언트 자격 증명은 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ClientCertificate%2A> 클래스의 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> 속성을 사용하여 지정해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-104">The client credential in the certificate case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ClientCertificate%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-105">username의 경우 클라이언트 자격 증명은 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.UserName%2A> 클래스의 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> 속성을 사용하여 지정해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-105">The client credential in the username case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.UserName%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-106">또한 메시지 보안 모드를 사용하는 경우 서비스 인증서를 사용하여 클라이언트를 제공해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-106">In addition, when message security mode is used, the client must be provisioned with the service's certificate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1a07e-107">이 경우 서비스 자격 증명은 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ServiceCertificate%2A> 클래스의 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> 속성을 사용하여 지정해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1a07e-107">The service credential in this case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ServiceCertificate%2A> property on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
   
  
